3) AS imp, toDecimal128(0, 3) AS auc, sumIf(if(s_asid = 0, fsr, 1), notEmpty(hbp) AND (iid = 0) AND (fid != 0)) AS hbi, sumIf(if(s_asid = 0, fsr, 1), ipx) AS pix, sumIf(if(s_asid = 0, fsr, 1), empty(hbp) AND (iid = 0) AND (fid != 0)) AS dpix FROM cte ARRAY JOIN asid AS s_asid, asus AS s_asus WHERE (lc = 1) AND ((flt = 0) OR ((flt >= 70) AND (flt < 90))) AND (irtb = 0) GROUP BY hr, pub, seg, usr, cnt, env, fmt, dev, del, tmp, rtb );
